```
GREEDY + MATH (3 lines of logic):
  chunks     = max_freq - 1
  idle_spots = chunks * n
  for each other task: idle_spots -= min(chunks, freq)
  return len(tasks) + max(0, idle_spots)

MAX HEAP (simulate n+1 rounds):
  each round: pick top min(n+1, heap_size) tasks
  add idle if heap not empty after round
  repeat until heap empty
